  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211010/extras/f078c57e88d77585f90d548982e2f659.poster.avif?t=1728425319\" width=560 height=75 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211010/extras/f078c57e88d77585f90d548982e2f659.webm?t=1728425319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Color Wheels is the solution to your color selection dilemma. This app, based on color wheel theory, helps you create harmonious color combinations quickly and easily. A color wheel is a tool used in color theory to visualize the relationships between colors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211010/extras/7a4de89a1411605cd445241be8a7ce1e.poster.avif?t=1728425319\" width=550 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211010/extras/7a4de89a1411605cd445241be8a7ce1e.webm?t=1728425319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211010/extras/7a4de89a1411605cd445241be8a7ce1e.mp4?t=1728425319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose a base color and watch as the app suggests elegant combinations, creating visually pleasing and balanced compositions based on your chosen color harmonies and color wheel type.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The app offers a variety of color wheels to choose from, ranging from Johannes Itten's gradient circle to Wilhelm Friedrich Oswald's circle, as well as circles with hue shifts, color temperature shifts, and color interpretations for print.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211010/extras/bbc330e8be32ad0f4310bcd323f3b028.poster.avif?t=1728425319\" width=550 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211010/extras/bbc330e8be32ad0f4310bcd323f3b028.webm?t=1728425319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211010/extras/bbc330e8be32ad0f4310bcd323f3b028.mp4?t=1728425319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can modify the color harmony and control the hue shift for each sample, seeing the changes directly on the wheel and in the color swatch set. This can significantly speed up the decision-making process for the color combination you'll use in your project.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211010/extras/299fe3aeac758497f88b99018227ee67.poster.avif?t=1728425319\" width=550 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211010/extras/299fe3aeac758497f88b99018227ee67.webm?t=1728425319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If your profession or hobby involves graphic design, web design, photography, videography, architectural visualization, or game development, this app is for you. Whether you're editing photos, painting, color grading videos, creating motion graphics, designing YouTube thumbnails, concept art, or 3D models for film and games, this app will help you find the perfect color solution with elegance and taste.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211010/extras/f078c57e88d77585f90d548982e2f659.poster.avif?t=1728425319\" width=560 height=75 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211010/extras/f078c57e88d77585f90d548982e2f659.webm?t=1728425319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Color Wheels is the solution to your color selection dilemma. This app, based on color wheel theory, helps you create harmonious color combinations quickly and easily. A color wheel is a tool used in color theory to visualize the relationships between colors.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211010/extras/7a4de89a1411605cd445241be8a7ce1e.poster.avif?t=1728425319\" width=550 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211010/extras/7a4de89a1411605cd445241be8a7ce1e.webm?t=1728425319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211010/extras/7a4de89a1411605cd445241be8a7ce1e.mp4?t=1728425319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose a base color and watch as the app suggests elegant combinations, creating visually pleasing and balanced compositions based on your chosen color harmonies and color wheel type.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The app offers a variety of color wheels to choose from, ranging from Johannes Itten's gradient circle to Wilhelm Friedrich Oswald's circle, as well as circles with hue shifts, color temperature shifts, and color interpretations for print.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211010/extras/bbc330e8be32ad0f4310bcd323f3b028.poster.avif?t=1728425319\" width=550 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211010/extras/bbc330e8be32ad0f4310bcd323f3b028.webm?t=1728425319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211010/extras/bbc330e8be32ad0f4310bcd323f3b028.mp4?t=1728425319\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can modify the color harmony and control the hue shift for each sample, seeing the changes directly on the wheel and in the color swatch set. This can significantly speed up the decision-making process for the color combination you'll use in your project.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211010/extras/299fe3aeac758497f88b99018227ee67.poster.avif?t=1728425319\" width=550 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3211010/extras/299fe3aeac758497f88b99018227ee67.webm?t=1728425319\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If your profession or hobby involves graphic design, web design, photography, videography, architectural visualization, or game development, this app is for you. Whether you're editing photos, painting, color grading videos, creating motion graphics, designing YouTube thumbnails, concept art, or 3D models for film and games, this app will help you find the perfect color solution with elegance and taste.</p>",
